description: Dudes and Dudettes of Detroit, if you’re in the mood for great Italian food, man, you’ve gotta check out this groovy van. You’ll be hard-pressed to find a tastier Panini or gourmet Gelato that you would adore more, and a taste of their vegan Sorbet is a wonderful way to improve your day. Using old-school recipes straight from Italy guarantees that every frozen treat you eat will be all natural, creamy, and full of flavor. Give yourself the excitations and stop by to pick up some good vibrations alongside your groovy gourmet goodies.
name: Good Vibrations Groovy Food & Gelato
